(2512, 'ENU', '英語學系', 'ENU0306', '神探福爾摩斯 （小說與電影）', '', 'This course\nintends to introduce to students selected canonical works of\nSherlock Holmes short stories and novels. We will also watch film\nadaptations of Sherlock Holmes stories. The major issues we will\ndiscuss include, among others, London, East End, opium dens,\nsailors, adventure stories, crime fiction, modern medicine,\nforensics, and Darwinism. We will also screen such early silent\nfilms as Broken Blossoms, inspired by Sherlock Holmes and set in\nEast End of London, and most recent Sherlock Holmes movies and BBC\nproduction of Sherlock Holmes set in the 21st century of Iphone,\ninternet, GPA, blog and crime scenes.', 2, NULL, 0, 0, 0, ''),
