(2569, 'ESU', '地球科學系', 'ESU0047', '宇宙觀的進展', '', 'The aim of\nthis course is to introduce the students to the concepts of modern\ncosmology (General Relativity, Hubble Law, Primordial\nNucleosynthesis, Cosmic Microwave Background, Dark matter and Dark\nEnergy, Structure formation), and help them answer these questions:\n•What are the basic components of the universe? •What are the basic\nphysical laws that govern the universe? •What is the size and age\nof the universe? •What’s the current theory on origin and evolution\nof the universe (big bang!), and what are the evidences that\nsupport that theory? •What is the nature of\nspace/time/matter/energy? •What about the “dark side” of the\nuniverse: black holes, cosmic dark ages, dark matter, dark energy?\n•How galaxies were formed? •What is a black-hole and what influence\nit has on galaxies? The first part of the course will be dedicated\nto introduce the students to these concepts via series of lecture,\nand in a second parts the student will practice their knowledge\nthrough research projects.', 3, NULL, 0, 0, 0, ''),
(2570, 'ESU', '地球科學系', 'ESU0049', '大氣熱力學', '簡芳菁', '教學目標：\n本課程先講授古典熱力學的基礎觀念，包括：純物質性質、功和熱、熱力學第一定律、熱力學第二定律、和entropy。然後講授大氣的熱力性質，包括：水氣和溼空氣熱力學、大氣熱力圖、及大氣的熱力過程等。\n1. 前言 2. 一些觀念和定義 3. 純物質性質 4. 功和熱 5. 熱力學第一定律 6. 熱力學第二定律 7. 熵 8.\n水氣和溼空氣熱力學 9. 大氣熱力圖 10. 大氣的熱力過程 講授與考核 作業及平時成績(30%) 期中考(30%) 期末考(40%)\n主要參考書籍： Iribarne, J. V. and W. L. Godson, 1981: Atmospheric\nthermodynamics. 2nd ed., Reidel Pub. Co., 259 pp. Wylen, G. J. V.,\nR. G. Sonntag and C. Borgnakke, 1994: Fundamentals of classical\nthermodynamics. 4th ed. John Wiley & Sons, Inc., 852 pp (Chap.\n1-7). 其他參考書籍： Bohren, C. F., and B. A. Albrecht, 1998: Atmospheric\nthermodynamics, Oxford, 402 pp. Riegel, C. A., 1992: Fundamentals\nof atmospheric dynamics and thermodyna-mics. World Scientific. 496\npp.', 3, NULL, 0, 0, 1, '沒有限制'),
